snippet.title: Sweet Little Parrot Gets A Baby Sister Who’s The Total Opposite | The Dodo
snippet.description:
This sweet parrot was feeling lonely, so his mom introduced a new member of the family, a baby sister — their introduction is adorable, and soon they discover how different the two parrots really are.
